commentary: McLaren to Ashwin, OUT there was a sound as the ball passed the batsman and McLaren and the umpire were convinced, Ashwin didn't seem so. It nipped back in and Ashwin was playing from the crease, there was a gap between pad and bat, could have taken the inside edge or the top of the pad. It certainly clipped the top of the pad, was there an edge as well? Not convincing. You could say that Ashwin was unlucky
